{"tid":1379654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺現場前線有時好難通知大部隊行動，建議用哨子作簡單指揮","createTime":"2019-07-28T23:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T23:38:41.000Z","uid":128995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1066d7d5cfd8d46ae43fbf41ebbf9644f78db5e","tid":1379654,"uid":128995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:03:52.000Z","msg":"中後排好多時只係睇住前面既人做乜佢地就做乜，後面一睇到前面走就迅速潰散<br />\n<br />\n係到建議用哨子作簡單指令<br />\n例如<br />\n吹1下 ＝向前<br />\n吹2下＝堅守<br />\n吹3下 ＝ 慢慢向後退<br />\n<br />\n睇到手足比人捉都係後退潰散果時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以點樣退好重要，認真要諗下簡單指揮保持陣型"},{"pid":"2fc4d1fb36656de7c8ae829cb25fa5b8c6b8acf8","tid":1379654,"uid":128995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:38:41.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}